{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":811,"text":"The 2011 Arab Spring"},{"time":2776,"text":"captured the attention of the world."},{"time":4579,"text":"It also captured the attention"},{"time":6228,"text":"of authoritarian governments in other countries,"},{"time":8605,"text":"who were worried that revolution would spread."},{"time":11568,"text":"To respond, they ramped up surveillance"},{"time":13645,"text":"of activists, journalists and dissidents"},{"time":16741,"text":"who they feared would inspire revolution"},{"time":18695,"text":"in their own countries."},{"time":20530,"text":"One prominent Bahraini activist,"},{"time":22575,"text":"who was arrested and tortured by his government,"},{"time":24685,"text":"has said that the interrogators showed him"},{"time":26410,"text":"transcripts of his telephone calls"},{"time":28280,"text":"and text messages."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30088,"text":"Of course, it's no secret"},{"time":31744,"text":"that governments are able to intercept\ntelephone calls and text messages."},{"time":34940,"text":"It's for that reason that many activists"},{"time":37312,"text":"specifically avoid using the telephone."},{"time":39238,"text":"Instead, they use tools like Skype,"},{"time":41586,"text":"which they think are immune to interception."},{"time":44106,"text":"They're wrong."},{"time":45878,"text":"There have now been over the last few years"},{"time":48604,"text":"an industry of companies"},{"time":50250,"text":"who provide surveillance technology to governments,"},{"time":53504,"text":"specifically technology that\nallows those governments"},{"time":55865,"text":"to hack into the computers"},{"time":57518,"text":"of surveillance targets."},{"time":59113,"text":"Rather than intercepting the communications \nas they go over the wire,"},{"time":61953,"text":"instead they now hack into your computer,"},{"time":64220,"text":"enable your webcam, enable your microphone,"},{"time":66222,"text":"and steal documents from your computer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68679,"text":"When the government of Egypt fell in 2011,"},{"time":71512,"text":"activists raided the office of the secret police,"},{"time":74913,"text":"and among the many documents they found"},{"time":76901,"text":"was this document by the Gamma Corporation,"},{"time":79218,"text":"by Gamma International."},{"time":81019,"text":"Gamma is a German company"},{"time":82676,"text":"that manufactures surveillance software"},{"time":84160,"text":"and sells it only to governments."},{"time":86317,"text":"It's important to note that most governments"},{"time":88324,"text":"don't really have the in-house capabilities"},{"time":90390,"text":"to develop this software."},{"time":91855,"text":"Smaller ones don't have the resources"},{"time":93474,"text":"or the expertise,"},{"time":95250,"text":"and so there's this market of Western companies"},{"time":98557,"text":"who are happy to supply them with the tools"},{"time":100524,"text":"and techniques for a price."},{"time":102242,"text":"Gamma is just one of these companies."},{"time":104848,"text":"I should note also that Gamma never actually sold"},{"time":107756,"text":"their software to the Egyptian government."},{"time":109653,"text":"They'd sent them an invoice for a sale,"},{"time":112250,"text":"but the Egyptians never bought it."},{"time":113892,"text":"Instead, apparently, the Egyptian government"},{"time":115616,"text":"used a free demo version of Gamma's software."},{"time":118249,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":121024,"text":"So this screenshot is from a sales video"},{"time":124522,"text":"that Gamma produced."},{"time":126087,"text":"Really, they're just emphasizing"},{"time":128070,"text":"in a relatively slick presentation"},{"time":129721,"text":"the fact that the police can sort of sit"},{"time":131914,"text":"in an air-conditioned office"},{"time":133364,"text":"and remotely monitor someone"},{"time":134775,"text":"without them having any idea that it's going on."},{"time":136950,"text":"You know, your webcam light won't turn on."},{"time":138985,"text":"There's nothing to indicate that\nthe microphone is enabled."}]},{"cues":[{"time":142339,"text":"This is the managing director\nof Gamma International."},{"time":145674,"text":"His name is Martin Muench."},{"time":147535,"text":"There are many photos of Mr. Muench that exist."},{"time":150466,"text":"This is perhaps my favorite."},{"time":152318,"text":"I'm just going to zoom in a little bit onto his webcam."},{"time":154462,"text":"You can see there's a little sticker"},{"time":156130,"text":"that's placed over his camera."},{"time":158023,"text":"He knows what kind of surveillance is possible,"},{"time":160556,"text":"and so clearly he doesn't want it to be used"},{"time":162362,"text":"against him."},{"time":163964,"text":"Muench has said that he intends"},{"time":165888,"text":"for his software to be used"},{"time":167552,"text":"to capture terrorists and locate pedophiles."},{"time":170535,"text":"Of course, he's also acknowledged that once"},{"time":172331,"text":"the software has been sold to governments,"},{"time":174486,"text":"he has no way of knowing how it can be used."},{"time":178311,"text":"Gamma's software has been located on servers"},{"time":180161,"text":"in countries around the world,"},{"time":181817,"text":"many with really atrocious track records"},{"time":184208,"text":"and human rights violations."},{"time":185769,"text":"They really are selling their\nsoftware around the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":189164,"text":"Gamma is not the only company in the business."},{"time":191465,"text":"As I said, it's a $5 billion industry."},{"time":194216,"text":"One of the other big guys in the industry"},{"time":197055,"text":"is an Italian company called Hacking Team."},{"time":199450,"text":"Now, Hacking Team has what is probably"},{"time":201175,"text":"the slickest presentation."},{"time":203145,"text":"The video they've produced is very sexy,"},{"time":206173,"text":"and so I'm going to play you a clip"},{"time":207821,"text":"just so you can get a feel"},{"time":209135,"text":"both for the capabilities of the software"},{"time":210966,"text":"but also how it's marketed"},{"time":212872,"text":"to their government clients."}]},{"cues":[{"time":214640,"text":"(Video) Narrator: You want to look \nthrough your target's eyes."},{"time":218179,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":220063,"text":"You have to hack your target."},{"time":223065,"text":"[\"While your target is browsing the web, exchanging documents, receiving SMS, crossing the borders\"]"},{"time":229381,"text":"You have to hit many different platforms."},{"time":232304,"text":"[\"Windows, OS X, iOS, Android,\nBlackberry, Symbian, Linux\"]"},{"time":236184,"text":"You have to overcome encryption"},{"time":238652,"text":"and capture relevant data."},{"time":241549,"text":"[Skype &amp; encrypted calls, target location, \nmessaging, relationships,"},{"time":246108,"text":"web browsing, audio &amp; video\"]"},{"time":249280,"text":"Being stealth and untraceable."},{"time":253440,"text":"[\"Immune to any protection system\nHidden collection infrastructure\"]"},{"time":256714,"text":"Deployed all over your country."},{"time":260819,"text":"[\"Up to hundreds of thousands of targets\nManaged from a single spot\"]"},{"time":265353,"text":"Exactly what we do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":268675,"text":"Christopher Soghoian: So, it\nwould be funny if it wasn't true,"},{"time":270938,"text":"but, in fact, Hacking Team's software"},{"time":272726,"text":"is being sold to governments around the world."},{"time":275674,"text":"Last year we learned, for example,"},{"time":277426,"text":"that it's been used to target Moroccan \njournalists by the Moroccan government."},{"time":281474,"text":"Many, many countries it's been found in."},{"time":284018,"text":"So, Hacking Team has also been actively courting"},{"time":287142,"text":"the U.S. law enforcement market."},{"time":289485,"text":"In the last year or so, the company"},{"time":291768,"text":"has opened a sales office in Maryland."},{"time":296544,"text":"The company has also hired a spokesperson."},{"time":298658,"text":"They've been attending"},{"time":300195,"text":"surveillance industry conferences"},{"time":301792,"text":"where law enforcement officials show up."},{"time":303807,"text":"They've spoken at the conferences."},{"time":305641,"text":"What I thought was most fascinating was"},{"time":307229,"text":"they've actually paid for the coffee break"},{"time":309330,"text":"at one of the law enforcement conferences"},{"time":311270,"text":"earlier this year."},{"time":312763,"text":"I can't tell you for sure that Hacking Team"},{"time":314862,"text":"has sold their technology in the United States,"},{"time":317587,"text":"but what I can tell you that if they haven't sold it,"},{"time":319558,"text":"it isn't because they haven't been trying hard."}]},{"cues":[{"time":322733,"text":"So as I said before,"},{"time":324775,"text":"governments that don't really have the resources"},{"time":326695,"text":"to build their own tools will buy"},{"time":328291,"text":"off-the-shelf surveillance software,"},{"time":329701,"text":"and so for that reason,"},{"time":331089,"text":"you see that the government of, say, Tunisia,"},{"time":333805,"text":"might use the same software\nas the government of Germany."},{"time":335993,"text":"They're all buying off-the-shelf stuff."},{"time":338265,"text":"The Federal Bureau of\nInvestigation in the United States"},{"time":340464,"text":"does have the budget to build\ntheir own surveillance technology,"},{"time":343226,"text":"and so for several years, I've been trying"},{"time":345007,"text":"to figure out if and how the FBI"},{"time":347398,"text":"is hacking into the computers of surveillance targets."}]},{"cues":[{"time":350296,"text":"My friends at an organization called\nthe Electronic Frontier Foundation --"},{"time":353449,"text":"they're a civil society group â€”"},{"time":355761,"text":"obtained hundreds of documents from the FBI"},{"time":358253,"text":"detailing their next generation\nof surveillance technologies."},{"time":361101,"text":"Most of these documents were heavily redacted,"},{"time":363735,"text":"but what you can see from the slides,"},{"time":366551,"text":"if I zoom in, is this term:"},{"time":368513,"text":"Remote Operations Unit."},{"time":370333,"text":"Now, when I first looked into this,"},{"time":372567,"text":"I'd never heard of this unit before."},{"time":374637,"text":"I've been studying surveillance\nfor more than six years."},{"time":376939,"text":"I'd never heard of it."},{"time":378224,"text":"And so I went online and I did some research,"},{"time":380187,"text":"and ultimately I hit the mother lode"},{"time":382312,"text":"when I went to LinkedIn,"},{"time":383946,"text":"the social networking site for job seekers."},{"time":386515,"text":"There were lots of former\nU.S. government contractors"},{"time":389428,"text":"who had at one point worked"},{"time":390815,"text":"for the Remote Operating Unit,"},{"time":392124,"text":"and were describing in surprising detail on their CVs"},{"time":395538,"text":"what they had done in their former job."},{"time":397569,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":399791,"text":"So I took this information"},{"time":401778,"text":"and I gave it to a journalist that I know\nand trust at the Wall Street Journal,"},{"time":405522,"text":"and she was able to contact several other"},{"time":407323,"text":"former law enforcement officials"},{"time":409077,"text":"who spoke on background and confirmed"},{"time":410883,"text":"that yes, in fact, the FBI has a dedicated team"},{"time":414242,"text":"that does nothing but hack into the computers"},{"time":416378,"text":"of surveillance targets."},{"time":417904,"text":"Like Gamma and Hacking Team,"},{"time":419792,"text":"the FBI also has the capability"},{"time":421909,"text":"to remotely activate webcams, microphones,"},{"time":425303,"text":"steal documents, get web browsing information,"},{"time":427505,"text":"the works."}]},{"cues":[{"time":429189,"text":"There's sort of a big problem"},{"time":431011,"text":"with governments going into hacking,"},{"time":432611,"text":"and that's that terrorists, pedophiles,"},{"time":435130,"text":"drug dealers, journalists and human rights activists"},{"time":438041,"text":"all use the same kinds of computers."},{"time":440312,"text":"There's no drug dealer phone"},{"time":442359,"text":"and there's no journalist laptop."},{"time":444325,"text":"We all use the same technology,"},{"time":446559,"text":"and what that means then is that for governments"},{"time":448453,"text":"to have the capability to hack into the computers"},{"time":450570,"text":"of the real bad guys,"},{"time":452269,"text":"they also have to have the capability"},{"time":454245,"text":"to hack into our devices too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":456430,"text":"So governments around the world"},{"time":458182,"text":"have been embracing this technology."},{"time":459643,"text":"They've been embracing hacking"},{"time":461248,"text":"as a law enforcement technique,"},{"time":463068,"text":"but without any real debate."},{"time":465018,"text":"In the United States, where I live,"},{"time":466837,"text":"there have been no congressional hearings."},{"time":468662,"text":"There's no law that's been passed"},{"time":470623,"text":"specifically authorizing this technique,"},{"time":472696,"text":"and because of its power and potential for abuse,"},{"time":475365,"text":"it's vital that we have an informed public debate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":478312,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":480258,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}